<p>
<note n="0953001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0953001">若作＝善得【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0953003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0953003">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0953004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0953004">趣＝起【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0953006" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0953006">則＝即【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0954001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0954001">作＝住【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0956001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0956001">心＝以【宋】【元】【明】</note>
